---
layout: base.njk
pageTitle: "Dekoris — Crafting Beautiful Spaces"
pageDescription: "Dekoris is a proudly Namibian, 100% female-owned interiors company specialising in blinds, curtains, wall panelling, décor, and soft finishes."
activePage: home
includeSnipcart: true
permalink: /
---

  <!-- ═══════════ HERO ═══════════ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-image"></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-label">Domestic & Professional Interiors</div>
      <h1>Crafting Beautiful Spaces</h1>
      <p>Blinds, curtains, and décor that elevate the beauty of your home and office. Proudly Namibian, 100% female-owned.</p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/quote/" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
        <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════ ABOUT ═══════════ -->
  <section class="section about">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-images fade-up">
          <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/06bb1b_2f184c440e2346d4bc27117ed561ee96~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_600,h_450,al_c,q_80,enc_avif,quality_auto/06bb1b_2f184c440e2346d4bc27117ed561ee96~mv2.jpg" alt="Venetian blinds installation">
          <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/06bb1b_7e48319a0d7b4169aa01f0916998faa4~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_600,h_450,al_c,q_80,enc_avif,quality_auto/06bb1b_7e48319a0d7b4169aa01f0916998faa4~mv2.jpg" alt="Roller blinds in modern room">
          <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/06bb1b_1cc1fc63dd804326b0cd0a539df6f1e8~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_600,h_450,al_c,q_80,enc_avif,quality_auto/06bb1b_1cc1fc63dd804326b0cd0a539df6f1e8~mv2.jpg" alt="Honeycomb blinds detail">
          <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/06bb1b_1033e929b8864988bb4213a6e7121966~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_600,h_450,al_c,q_80,enc_avif,quality_auto/06bb1b_1033e929b8864988bb4213a6e7121966~mv2.jpg" alt="Zebra blinds in living room">
        </div>
        <div class="about-text fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.15s">
          <div class="section-label">About Us</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2>
          <p>Dekoris is a leading, 100% female-owned Namibian provider of high-quality blinds and curtain installation services for residential, commercial, and institutional spaces.</p>
          <p>With a commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction, we offer tailored window treatment solutions to enhance the aesthetic and functional aspects of any environment.</p>
          <div class="highlight">To deliver inspiring spaces that enrich lives, blending timeless design with a modern Namibian spirit.</div>
          <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-gold" style="margin-top: 8px;">Our Story</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════ VALUE PROPS ═══════════ -->
  <section class="values">
    <div class="values-inner">
      <div class="value-item fade-up">
        <div class="value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
